Yahoo! Messenger
----------------

* Preferences -> Uncheck "Show Yahoo! Messenger Insider"
* Preferences -> Privacy -> Uncheck "Idle Status"
* Preferences -> Privacy -> Change my status:
  * Uncheck "Playing a game"
  * Uncheck "Showing my webcam"
* Preferences -> Messaging -> Conversation Style: Simple
* Preferences -> Messaging -> Enable Message Archiving
* Preferences -> Messaging -> Enable Chat Room Archiving
* Preferences -> Alerts -> Uncheck "Enable alert sounds"
* Preferences -> Display Image -> None
* View -> Uncheck "Show Groups"
* View -> Sort By Name
